  '<h3 id="retry-circuit">new b.retry.CircuitBreaker(name, opts) <a class="anchor" href="#retry-circuit">#</a></h3>',
  '<p>Wraps a callable in a half-open / open / closed state machine: when an upstream is consistently failing, the breaker trips open and short-circuits new calls without burning attempts. After a cooldown the breaker enters half-open and probes; <code>successThreshold</code> consecutive probes re-close it.</p>',
